      <title>爱尔兰危机时期的坏账银行制定了 2025 年关闭计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/ireland-s-crisis-era-bad-bank-sets-out-plan-to-wind-down-in-2025</link>
