    <item>
      <title>报告称英国疾病危机始于紧缩政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/britain-s-sickness-crisis-began-during-austerity-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项研究发现，英国的健康问题始于紧缩时期，并使其经济更容易受到新冠疫情的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/britain-s-sickness-crisis-began-during-austerity-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 10:01:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普内阁人选准备接受参议院确认听证会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/trump-cabinet-picks-senate-confirmation-hearings-scheduled-so-far</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国候任总统唐纳德·特朗普的提名人将于下周开始在美国参议院作证，共和党急于在 1 月 20 日的就职典礼后尽快组建新内阁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/trump-cabinet-picks-senate-confirmation-hearings-scheduled-so-far</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芬兰称被扣押的影子舰队油轮不适合航行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/finland-says-detained-shadow-fleet-tanker-is-not-seaworthy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芬兰当局对被扣押的这艘载有俄罗斯石油的油轮进行检查后，认定其不适合航海。]]></description>
